{"tid":215331,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【新手媽咪】吳若希初餵人奶成個鐘 爆囡囡食唔停﹕啖啖大大力啜","createTime":"2017-04-24T10:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T09:03:10.000Z","uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c81d4efe59784246a044e817752efb9bead9f8bd","tid":215331,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170424&amp;guid=56605251&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170424%26guid%3D56605251%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=03c8cc12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170424%26guid%3D56605251%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=d2fd28cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170424&amp;guid=56605251&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n24歲吳若希噚日為澳門闊少男友Alex Ho誕下囡囡Giselle，生B女過程好辛苦，痛足22個鐘頭，但吳若希都冇得休息，佢噚日接受大台電話訪問時透露囡囡好為食，佢話：「B女好特別，通常初生BB會成日喊，但Giselle喊兩聲就會靜落嚟，眼仔睩睩周圍望。佢仲叻到一出世會搵奶奶飲，冇嘢需要好擔心。」<br />\n<br />\n吳若希仲好勤力咁更新Ig，噚晚貼完囡囡腳印仔相，今朝約7點鐘又影咗病房內環境相，雖然全房拉晒窗簾好暗，但啱啱天光，透出室外陽光，吳若希留言﹕「餵咗成個鐘人奶，我個女仲係要繼續食～仲要啖啖大大力啜～～有冇咁大食？！」佢仲hashtag咗「都話我有咗嘅時候唔係我肚餓」、「一生完即刻胃口大減」、「我唔係姓賴」、「小姓吳」、「何家千金胃口大」，睇嚟吳若希都冇覺好瞓，唔少粉絲都為佢加油，仲教佢瞓响度餵人奶條腰無咁辛苦，又可以休息下添。"},{"pid":"9a2b79ac03acb3bffb7ecf8dc6241de57bbc75c9","tid":215331,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eda6f4624a634a7871fef7a7b8d538544739cef","tid":215331,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"太細 啜唔到？"},{"pid":"680